_sText:
Breakfloor_Quantum_Entanglement
Fps:100+ on standstill
Fps:50+ when blocks are rapidly being destroyed

The reason behind the name is simple.
yes it is a break floor.
but each breakable block is tied to a counterpart on the opposite side of the map so when one of them is destoryed the other one is aswell.

Fun Behind it All?
You can shoot the floor out from under your enemies across the map by shooting parts of the floor on your side. Awesome...
